to add some slapstick...

786
00:54:29,466 --> 00:54:31,331
and the movie laid an egg.

787
00:54:31,434 --> 00:54:34,335
A great, expensive bomb
for which I was blamed.

788
00:54:35,438 --> 00:54:38,202
