all so long ago.

793
00:54:52,188 --> 00:54:54,088
Fifteen years.

794
00:54:57,494 --> 00:55:00,827
Making movies is
the most wonderful thing in the world.

795
00:55:03,500 --> 00:55:07,061
Working with friends,
entertaining people.

796
00:55:07,170 --> 00:55:09,070
Yes,
I suppose I miss it.

797
00:55:11,041 --> 00:55:13,100
But I chose freedom.

798
00:55:15,211 --> 00:55:18,044
David, of course,
was still in the thick of it,

799
00:55:18,181 --> 00:55:21,082
